# 🚀 QuickBlog

QuickBlog is a full-stack blogging platform built with the MERN stack. It allows users to explore blogs, search by category, read detailed articles, and interact through comments, while providing administrators with a dedicated dashboard to create, manage, and publish content.

This project was built to gain hands-on experience with real-world full-stack development by combining frontend, backend, database, authentication, AI integration, and media management into a single application.

---

# ✨ Features

## Public Website

* Browse published blogs
* Search blogs by title
* Filter blogs by category
* Read complete blog articles
* Leave comments on blogs
* Responsive design for all devices

## Admin Dashboard

* Secure JWT-based admin authentication
* Dashboard with blog and comment statistics
* Create new blogs
* Save blogs as drafts
* Publish or unpublish blogs
* Edit existing blogs
* Delete blogs
* Manage comments
* Generate blog content using Google Gemini AI
* Upload and optimize images using ImageKit

