# Challenges I Faced

Building this project involved much more than implementing CRUD operations. One of the biggest challenges was structuring the backend using the MVC pattern while keeping the code organized and maintainable. Integrating Google Gemini AI for content generation, handling image uploads through ImageKit, implementing draft and publish functionality, protecting admin routes with JWT authentication, and synchronizing the frontend with backend APIs were all valuable learning experiences.

Working through these challenges helped me better understand how different parts of a full-stack application communicate with each other and how real-world applications are structured.

